=== 发展 ===
[[File:Tim_Berners-Lee_April_2009.jpg|缩略图]]  ]]
1980年，物理学家[[蒂姆·伯纳斯-李|蒂姆·伯纳斯-李]]在[[歐洲核子研究組織|欧洲核子研究中心]]（CERN）在承包工程期间，为使CERN的研究人员使用并-{zh-hans:共享; zh-hant:共享}-文档，他提出并创建原型系统[[ENQUIRE|ENQUIRE]]。1989年，伯纳斯-李在一份备忘录中提出一个基于[[互联网|互联网]]的[[超文本|超文本]]系统<ref>Tim Berners-Lee, "Information Management: A Proposal." CERN (March 1989, May 1990). [http://www.w3.org/History/1989/proposal.html W3.org] {{Wayback|url=http://www.w3.org/History/1989/proposal.html |date=20100401051011 }}</ref>。他-{zh-hans:规定; zh-hant:制定}-HTML并在1990年底写出浏览器和服务器软件。同年，伯纳斯-李与CERN的数据系统工程师[[罗伯特·卡里奥|罗伯特·卡里奥]]联合为项目申请资助，但未被CERN正式批准。在他的个人笔记中<ref>Tim Berners-Lee, [http://www.w3.org/DesignIssues/ "Design Issues"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.w3.org/DesignIssues/ |date=20090503080104 }}</ref>伯纳斯-李列举“一些使用超文本的领域”，并把百科全书列为-{zh-hans:首位; zh-hant:第一項}-<ref>Tim Berners-Lee,  [http://www.w3.org/DesignIssues/Uses.html "Design Issues"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.w3.org/DesignIssues/Uses.html |date=20090625041233 }}</ref>。

HTML的-{zh-hans:首个; zh-hant:首次}-公开描述出现于一个名为HTML Tags<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://info.cern.ch/hypertext/WWW/MarkUp/Tags.html |title=HTML Tags |access-date=2021-06-29 |archive-date=2019-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191116160051/http://info.cern.ch/hypertext/WWW/MarkUp/Tags.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>的文件中，由蒂姆·伯纳斯-李于1991年底提及<ref name="tagshtml"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://lists.w3.org/Archives/Public/www-talk/1991SepOct/0003.html|title=First mention of HTML Tags on the www-talk mailing list|publisher=World Wide Web Consortium|date=1991-10-29|accessdate=2007-04-08|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070224040625/http://lists.w3.org/Archives/Public/www-talk/1991SepOct/0003.html|archivedate=2007-02-24}}</ref>。它描述18个元素，包括HTML初始的、相对简单的设计。除了超链接标签外，其他设计都深受CERN内部一个以[[SGML|标准通用标记语言]]（SGML）为基础的文件格式SGMLguid的影响。这些元素仍有11个存在于HTML 4中<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.w3.org/TR/1999/REC-html401-19991224/index/elements|title=Index of elements in HTML 4|publisher=World Wide Web Consortium|date=1999-12-24|accessdate=2007-04-08|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070505172415/http://www.w3.org/TR/1999/REC-html401-19991224/index/elements|archivedate=2007-05-05}}</ref>。

伯纳斯-李认为HTML是SGML的一个应用程序。1993年中期[[互联网工程任务组|互联网工程任务组]]（IETF）发布首个HTML规范的提案：[http://www.w3.org/MarkUp/draft-ietf-iiir-html-01.txt “超文本标记语言（HTML）”互联网草案]{{Wayback|url=http://www.w3.org/MarkUp/draft-ietf-iiir-html-01.txt |date=20090415045944 }}，由伯纳斯-李与{{Le|丹·康纳利|Dan Connolly (computer scientist)}}撰写。其中包括一个SGML[[文件类型描述|文档类型定义]]来定义语法<ref>{{cite web|url=http://lists.w3.org/Archives/Public/www-talk/1991NovDec/0020.html|title=Re: SGML/HTML docs, X Browser (archived www-talk mailing list post)|author=Tim Berners-Lee|date=1991-12-09|accessdate=2007-06-16|quote=SGML is very general. HTML is a specific application of the SGML basic syntax applied to hypertext documents with simple structure.|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071222060359/http://lists.w3.org/Archives/Public/www-talk/1991NovDec/0020.html|archivedate=2007-12-22}}</ref>。草案于6个月后过期，不过值得注意的是其对[[NCSA_Mosaic|NCSA Mosaic]]浏览器嵌入在线图像的自定义标签的认可，这反映IETF把标准立足于成功原型的理念<ref name="raymond">{{cite book |url=http://www.faqs.org/docs/artu/ |chapterurl=http://www.faqs.org/docs/artu/ietf_process.html |title=The Art of Unix Programming |last=Raymond |first=Eric |chapter=IETF and the RFC Standards Process |quote=In IETF tradition, standards have to arise from experience with a working prototype implementation — but once they become standards, code that does not conform to them is considered broken and mercilessly scrapped. ...Internet-Drafts are not specifications; software implementers and vendors are specifically barred from claiming compliance with them as if they were specifications. Internet-Drafts are focal points for discussion, usually in a working group... Once an Internet-Draft has been published with an RFC number, it is a specification to which implementers may claim conformance. It is expected that the authors of the RFC and the community at large will begin correcting the specification with field experience. |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20050317014053/http://www.faqs.org/docs/artu/ |archivedate=2005-03-17 |access-date=2016-01-22 }}</ref>。同样，{{Le|戴夫·拉格特|Dave Raggett}}在1993年末提出的与之竞争的互联网草案“HTML+（超文本标记格式）”建议规范已经实现的功能，如表格与填写表单<ref name="html+">{{cite web |url=https://datatracker.ietf.org/public/idindex.cgi?command=id_detail&id=789 |title=HTML+ Internet-Draft — Abstract |quote=Browser writers are experimenting with extensions to HTML and it is now appropriate to draw these ideas together into a revised document format. The new format is designed to allow a gradual roll over from HTML, adding features like tables, captioned figures and fill-out forms for querying remote databases or mailing questionnaires. |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=http://arquivo.pt/wayback/20160515150537/https://datatracker.ietf.org/public/idindex.cgi?command=id_detail&id=789 |archivedate=2016-05-15 |accessdate=2016-01-22 }}</ref>。

在HTML和HTML+的草案于1994年初到期后，IETF创建一个HTML工作组，并在1995年完成"HTML 2.0"，这是第一个旨在成为对其后续实现标准的依据的HTML规范<ref>{{cite web |first1=Tim |last1=Berners-Lee |first2=Daniel |last2=Connelly |url=http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc1866 |title=RFC 1866 – Hypertext Markup Language – 2.0 |publisher=Internet Engineering Task Force |date=November 1995 |accessdate=2010-12-01 |quote=This document thus defines an HTML 2.0 (to distinguish it from the previous informal specifications). Future (generally upwardly compatible) versions of HTML with new features will be released with higher version numbers. |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110827085509/http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc1866 |archivedate=2011-08-27 }}</ref>。

在IETF的-{zh-hans:主持; zh-hant:主導}-下，HTML标准的进一步发展因竞争利益而遭受停滞。自1996年起，HTML规范一直由[[万维网联盟|万维网联盟]]（W3C）维护，并由商业软件厂商出资<ref name="raggett">{{cite book|first=Dave|last=Raggett|title=Raggett on HTML 4|year=1998|url=http://www.w3.org/People/Raggett/book4/ch02.html|accessdate=2007-07-09|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070625011525/http://www.w3.org/People/Raggett/book4/ch02.html|archivedate=2007-06-25}}</ref>。不过在2000年，HTML也成为国际标准（[[國際標準化組織|ISO]]/ [[IEC|IEC]]15445：2000）。HTML 4.01于1999年末发布，进一步的勘误版本于2001年发布。2004年，[[網頁超文本技術工作小組|网页超文本应用技术工作小组]]（WHATWG）开始开发HTML5，并在2008年与W3C共同-{zh-hans:交付; zh-hant:提出}-，2014年10月28日完成标准化<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.w3.org/2014/10/html5-rec.html.en |title=HTML5 – Hypertext Markup Language – 5.0 |publisher=Internet Engineering Task Force |date=2014-10-28 |accessdate=2014-11-25 |quote=This document recommends HTML 5.0 after completion. |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141102002517/http://www.w3.org/2014/10/html5-rec.html.en |archivedate=2014-11-02 }}</ref>。

